      <title>Hexo-Butterfly下的Markdown格式</title>
      <link href="/2021/11/04/technique/other/markdown/"/>
      <url>/2021/11/04/technique/other/markdown/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="note warning flat"><p>以下markdown使用方法并不全面，本人把觉得有用的挑出来了，需要了解全面请自行查看相关文档</p></div><h1 id="准备环境"><a href="#准备环境" class="headerlink" title="准备环境"></a>准备环境</h1><p><a href="https://typora.io/" title="https://typora.io/">Typera</a>：推荐使用这个工具编写markdown，当然vscode，记事本之类的也可以<br><a href="https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly" title="https://github.com/jerryc127/hexo-theme-butterfly">hexo-butterfly</a>：网站框架和主题，主题使用方法也在<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/dc584b87/" title="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/dc584b87/">官方文档</a> 中</p><h1 id="文章顶部"><a href="#文章顶部" class="headerlink" title="文章顶部"></a>文章顶部</h1><p>markdown文件必须都要写的，用以指定该文章的各种属性</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 标题（必填）</span><br><span class="line">date: year-month-day hour:min:sec（必填）</span><br><span class="line">updated: year-month-day hour:min:sec</span><br><span class="line">tags: 标签</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 第一层</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">  -</span> 第二层</span><br><span class="line">keywords: 关键字</span><br><span class="line">description: 描述</span><br><span class="line">top<span class="emphasis">_img: /img/topImg.png#顶部图片(false不显示)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">comments: false#显示评论</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">cover: /img/coverImg.png#文章缩略图(如果没有设置top_</span>img,文章页顶部将显示缩略图)</span><br><span class="line">toc: false#显示文章TOC(toc是侧边栏的那个目录，默认为设置中toc的enable配置)</span><br><span class="line">toc<span class="emphasis">_number:#显示toc_</span>number(默认为设置中toc的number配置)</span><br><span class="line">copyright:#版权(默认为设置中post<span class="emphasis">_copyright的enable配置)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">copyright_</span>author:#文章作者</span><br><span class="line">copyright<span class="emphasis">_author_</span>href:#作者链接</span><br><span class="line">copyright<span class="emphasis">_url:#文章链接</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">copyright_</span>info:#版权声明文字</span><br><span class="line">mathjax:</span><br><span class="line">katex:</span><br><span class="line">aplayer:</span><br><span class="line">highlight<span class="emphasis">_shrink:#代码框是否展开</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="emphasis">aside:#显示侧边栏</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h1><h2 id="二号标题"><a href="#二号标题" class="headerlink" title="二号标题"></a>二号标题</h2><h3 id="三号标题"><a href="#三号标题" class="headerlink" title="三号标题"></a>三号标题</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># 一号标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="section">## 二号标题</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h1><ol><li>有序列表1<ul><li>无序列表1</li><li>无序列表2</li></ul></li><li>有序列表2<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">1.</span> 有序列表</span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">   *</span> 无序列表</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><blockquote><p>引用</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&gt;引用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="链接"><a href="#链接" class="headerlink" title="链接"></a>链接</h1><p><a href="https://blog.betnke.xyz/" title="blog.betnke.xyz">betnke</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">显示文字</span>](<span class="link">网址 &quot;鼠标放上后的提示文字&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h1><p><img src="/img/base/favicon.png" alt="这是什么东西" title="小豆芽儿"></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片下的文字</span>](<span class="link">在source开始的图片路径，如/img/beanSprout.png &quot;鼠标放上后的提示文字&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Note"><a href="#Note" class="headerlink" title="Note"></a>Note</h1><p>风格:simple/modern/flat/disabled</p><div class="note primary flat"><p>类似引用，多了可选的预设</p></div><p>类型:default / primary / success / info / warning / danger </p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note 类型 风格 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">内容</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note red icon flat"><i class="note-icon fab fa-github"></i><p>背景颜色和图标</p></div><p>颜色:red orange green blue … 或<a href="https://www.sioe.cn/yingyong/yanse-rgb-16/" title="https://www.sioe.cn/yingyong/yanse-rgb-16/">十六进制颜色</a><br>图标:<a href="https://fontawesome.com/v5.15/icons?d=gallery&p=2&q=github" title="https://fontawesome.com/v5.15/icons?d=gallery&amp;p=2&amp;q=github">图标搜索网站</a> 搜索出想要的图标点开找到 如”fab fa-github”，填入’图标’</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note 颜色 图标 风格 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">内容</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="tag-hide"><a href="#tag-hide" class="headerlink" title="tag-hide"></a>tag-hide</h1><p>颜色:red orange green blue … 或<a href="https://www.sioe.cn/yingyong/yanse-rgb-16/" title="https://www.sioe.cn/yingyong/yanse-rgb-16/">十六进制颜色</a></p><span class="hide-inline"><button type="button" class="hide-button button--animated" style="background-color: #FF7242;color: #fff">猜猜我是谁  </button><span class="hide-content">皮卡丘</span></span><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% hideInline 內容,按钮文字(可空),背景色(可空),文字色(可空) %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="Tabs"><a href="#Tabs" class="headerlink" title="Tabs"></a>Tabs</h1><div class="tabs" id=""><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#-1"><i class="fab fa-github"></i>第一个表</button></li><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#-2">第二个表</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content" id="-1"><p><strong>1</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content active" id="-2"><p><strong>2</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs 名字(可空), 2(默认选第二个) %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab 第一个表(表名) @fab fa-github(图标) --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">内容1</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- tab 第二个表 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">内容2</span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="高亮文字"><a href="#高亮文字" class="headerlink" title="高亮文字"></a>高亮文字</h1><p>高<mark class="hl-label red">亮</mark> 文字<br>颜色:red orange green blue … 或<a href="https://www.sioe.cn/yingyong/yanse-rgb-16/" title="https://www.sioe.cn/yingyong/yanse-rgb-16/">十六进制颜色</a></p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% label 内容 颜色 %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
